# 🎯 Day 52 - Interactive Spotlight & Random Text Reveal
live link =  http://htmlpreview.github.io/?https://github.com/rhlydv215481/BASIC_to_advance_MEARNSTACK/blob/main/dom/day52/index.html
A modern interactive landing page built using **HTML**, **SCSS**, and **JavaScript**.

This project combines a **mouse-following spotlight effect**, **animated hover panels**, and a **random text reveal animation** to create an engaging UI experience.

