# 📖 Project Flow

```
Page Load
      │
      ▼
Three Video Panels
      │
      ▼
Move Mouse
      │
      ▼
JavaScript updates CSS Variables
(--x, --y)
      │
      ▼
CSS Radial Gradient moves
with the mouse
      │
      ▼
Hover on Heading
      │
      ▼
Original Text Saved
      │
      ▼
Random Letters Generated
      │
      ▼
After 2 Seconds
      │
      ▼
Original Text Restored
```

